Normal use:
    Expected result: User should be able to add competitors, start a race in whichever racetype they want, stop the clock for individual contestants, save and load the results from previous race.
    Result: Works as intended

Name with abnormal characters:
    Expected result: Name shall appear with given chars.
    Result: Name is handled as intended and displayed with abnormal chars.

Open 2 instances of the program and end one race, than the other:
    Expected result: Unless moved the exported competitors.xml will be overwritten.
    Result: As expected.

Manually removing the competitors xml while having it loaded.
    Expected result: Nothing out of the ordinary.
    Result: Nothing happens.